      <div class="lid" id="lid">

        <div class="face cover" id="cover">
          <div class="spine"><span>COOKIE · 뉴진스 · REEL 02 · CJ-0220</span></div>
          <div class="bk">
            <div class="jk-top"><span class="jk-kr">뉴진스</span><span class="jk-ser">LOOK BOOK 02</span></div>
            <div class="jk-art">
              <!-- printed, not drawn: same crust as the canvas cookie and the disc doodle,
                   but struck in one navy line. the object that opened the reel, on the cover. -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 34 34" aria-hidden="true">
                <ellipse class="ring" cx="17" cy="17" rx="15.6" ry="15.1" transform="rotate(-7 17 17)"/>
                <path class="crust" d="M31 17 C31.06 18.1 30.9 19.3 30.54 20.34 C30.19 21.38 29.45 22.3 28.88 23.24 C28.31 24.17 27.81 25.13 27.12 25.97 C26.43 26.8 25.64 27.6 24.77 28.25 C23.89 28.9 22.89 29.42 21.88 29.87 C20.87 30.31 19.78 30.81 18.69 30.93 C17.6 31.04 16.42 30.79 15.36 30.54 C14.29 30.29 13.31 29.81 12.28 29.43 C11.26 29.06 10.16 28.82 9.21 28.28 C8.27 27.74 7.38 26.99 6.64 26.18 C5.9 25.37 5.27 24.4 4.76 23.43 C4.24 22.45 3.75 21.38 3.56 20.31 C3.37 19.24 3.55 18.09 3.61 17 C3.68 15.91 3.79 14.87 3.96 13.79 C4.13 12.7 4.19 11.51 4.63 10.51 C5.08 9.51 5.86 8.61 6.62 7.81 C7.39 7.01 8.29 6.31 9.21 5.72 C10.14 5.13 11.14 4.59 12.17 4.26 C13.2 3.93 14.31 3.89 15.39 3.74 C16.47 3.59 17.56 3.35 18.66 3.36 C19.76 3.37 20.98 3.43 21.99 3.83 C23.01 4.23 23.91 5.04 24.77 5.74 C25.63 6.44 26.43 7.19 27.14 8.02 C27.84 8.85 28.5 9.74 29 10.7 C29.5 11.66 29.81 12.71 30.15 13.76 C30.48 14.81 30.93 15.9 31 17 Z"/>
                <circle class="chip" cx="12.4" cy="11.6" r="2.3"/><circle class="chip" cx="21.9" cy="13.2" r="1.6"/>
                <circle class="chip" cx="16" cy="17.6" r="2.5"/><circle class="chip" cx="23" cy="21.4" r="1.9"/>
                <circle class="chip" cx="11.3" cy="21.9" r="1.7"/><circle class="chip" cx="17.6" cy="25.3" r="1.2"/>
                <circle class="chip" cx="9.8" cy="16.4" r="1.1"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="jk-title">COOKIE</h3>
            <div class="jk-foot"><span>2:13 → 2:20 · INSPIRED LOOK</span><span class="endtag">2:20:00 — next look ↓</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="plastic" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="face inside">
          <div class="spine"><span>TYPE · COLOR · LAYOUT</span></div>
          <div class="bk ib">
            <div class="ib-head"><span class="ib-kick">Look 02 · 2:16</span><span class="ib-ser">B/W 2:20:00</span></div>
            <h2>그리고,<br>파랑.<svg class="ib-ul" viewBox="0 0 170 12" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 8 q24 -8 50 -1 q26 7 54 -2 q28 -8 60 1"/></svg></h2>
            <p class="lede">Cookie MV 2:13–2:20에서 가져온 컷. 전기 블루 필드, 그 위에 뜨는 방송용 크롬 타이포.<br><span style="opacity:.62">A cut borrowed from Cookie MV 2:13–2:20. Electric blue field, broadcast chrome type on top.</span></p>
            <ol class="tl">
              <li><b>1</b><span>type</span></li>
              <li><b>2</b><span>color</span></li>
              <li class="on"><b>3</b><span>layout</span></li>
            </ol>
            <!-- the small print a real back cover carries. it is also the honest place to say
                 what this is: a look study, not a release. -->
            <p class="ib-fine">Inspired by the Cookie MV, 2:13–2:20.<br>A look study. Not affiliated with ADOR or NewJeans.<br>Authored on a 1200×900 stage · scroll-scrubbed</p>
            <div class="ib-foot">
              <div class="barcode" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <div class="ib-cat">CJ-0220 · REEL 02</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      </div></div></div>

    </div>

    <div class="bug" id="bug" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="lz"><span class="n1">NEW</span><span class="n2">JEANS</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grain"></div>
    <div class="vig"></div>
    <div class="scan" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="reel"><span class="dot"></span> COOKIE · 뉴진스 &nbsp;— &nbsp;REEL 02</div>
      <div class="shot" id="shot">암전 · black</div>
    </div>

